"jannat injeneriyasi" deb ataydi.

00:04:34.133 --> 00:04:37.337
Biroq qayg'usiz dunyoda bitta muammo bor.

00:04:37.337 --> 00:04:40.120
G'orlarda yashagan ajdodlarimiz va

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:42.886
sevimli shoirlarimiz bunday dunyoni 
xohlashmagan bo'lardi.

00:04:43.022 --> 00:04:45.439
